<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<% include html_header.ejs %>
</head>
<body>
	<% include body_header.ejs %>
	
	<div class="jumbotron">
		<h1>新投票場作成フォーム</h1>
		<p class="lead">新しく投票場を作る画面です。</p>
	</div>

	<div class="container">

		<form class="" role="form" action="/create" method="post">

			<h2>管理用の情報を入力ください</h2>
			<hr>
			<div class="form-group row">
				<label for="email" class="col-xs-8 col-sm-2 control-label">メールアドレス</label>
				<div class="col-sm-8">
					<input type="text" placeholder="Email" class="form-control ">
				</div>
			</div>
			<br>
			<div class="form-group row">
				<label for="password" class="col-xs-8 col-sm-2 control-label">パスワード</label>
				<div class="col-sm-8 ">
					<input type="password" placeholder="Password" class="form-control">
				</div>
				<div class="col-xs-offset- col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8">
					<input type="password2" placeholder="again" class="form-control">
				</div>
			</div>

			
			<h2>投票用の情報を入力ください</h2>
			<hr>
			<div class="form-group row">
				<label for="title" class="col-xs-8 col-sm-2 control-label">タイトル</label>
				<div class="col-sm-8">
					<input type="text" placeholder="Email" class="form-control ">
				</div>
			</div>
			<br>

			<div class="row"> 
				<label for="explain" class="col-xs-8 col-sm-2 control-label">詳細</label>
				<div class="col-sm-8">
					<textarea class="form-control" rows="2" placeholder="詳細"></textarea>
				</div>
			</div>
			<br>
			<br>

			<div class="form-group row">
				<label for="contents" class="col-xs-8 col-sm-2 control-label">コンテンツ</label>
				<div class="col-sm-8 ">
					<textarea class="form-control" rows="3" placeholder="投票コンテンツの作成"></textarea>
				</div>
			</div>


			<div class="bs-example"> 
				<div class="row">
					<p class="col-sm-2 ">
						コンテンツの書き方　なんか、うまくコンテンツを作るフォームを考えないと
					</p>
					<p class="col-sm-4">
						# make select box<br>					
						> select,java,ruby,bash<br>
						# make comment box<br>
						> comment,感想
					</p>
					<div class="col-sm-3">
						<select class="form-control">
							<option value="java">java</option>
							<option value="ruby">ruby</option>
							<option value="bash">bash</option>
						</select>
						<textarea class="form-control" rows="2" placeholder="感想"></textarea>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<br>
			<button type="submit" class="btn-lg btn-success">Submit</button>
		</form>
	</div>

	<% include body_footer.ejs %>

</body>
</html>